    title: "The Pirate",
    titleZh: "\u6D77\u76D7",
    slug: "the-pirate",
    languageCode: "en",
    authorSlug: "walter-scott",
    description:
      "Set in the remote Shetland and Orkney Islands during the late seventeenth century, the novel follows the rivalry between two young men \u2014 Mordaunt Mertoun and the charismatic pirate Cleveland \u2014 for the affections of the sisters Minna and Brenda Troil. Scott draws on Norse mythology and island customs to create a vivid portrait of a society caught between lawful commerce and the allure of freebootery.",
